{"tid":40242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國式的邏輯思維","createTime":"2016-12-15T05:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T14:12:45.000Z","uid":34286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f59ba9a841ddcb2b5ce9d19eba0ea2e3ef10dd1","tid":40242,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:39:36.000Z","msg":"其他國家到中國投資，是中國恩賜他們，給他們機會賺錢；<br />\n中國到其他地方投資，是中國打救他們經濟，振興他們經濟；<br />\n中國員工為老細打工，屈老細錢是天公地道，因為老細是無良的；<br />\n中國老細請員工為他們打工，老細認為這是一種恩賜；<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n當年清朝時，林則徐銷鴉片，不賣茶葉給洋子，取消這種恩賜，覺得洋子會便祕而死；洋鬼子則認為這只不過是交易，不和你買，可以向錫蘭買"},{"pid":"fc63d669fa2413390ff6957f9dc62ed52cb7abb7","tid":40242,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:45:03.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72ea9f6a099f18abea86753119d02be8c95b6db2","tid":40242,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T13:34:03.000Z","msg":"樂觀SIR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f07c984039222a3ea7d4f48f7645d37fc19a73","tid":40242,"uid":52953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T13:57:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樂觀SIR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樂觀SIR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a31d7c4d781bb8a22503b21e04dbd9f7f16b58","tid":40242,"uid":28913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T13:59:00.000Z","msg":"覺得好真而留名"},{"pid":"11176a475027721d9ab5d7937d9a29111b0e8a42","tid":40242,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:11:14.000Z","msg":"👍"},{"pid":"4b7032e47fa9d8fbde7148f6c5b47f179c9b22fd","tid":40242,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:12:45.000Z","msg":"一言中的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}